Anyone else miss the old Wizards Community Forums? That screenshot was taken Sep 2015, about a month before the site was taken down. My post count reached about 3k during that last month cause I got really into the "you make the card" section. These are the last pics I have from the site before Wizards decided it wasn't worth it to keep it up/maintain it.. 😐 to my understanding a lot of the community has moved to nogoblinsallowed and/or mtgsalvation, but I've been reluctant to make an account on one of those for some reason. Oh well, one of these days I'll get back into mtg forums, but not now, got a lot going on atm. #mtg #wizards #community #forums #rip
